<TITLE>Samuel Guthrie (United States physician)</TITLE>

<PARAGRAPH>
<REF MENTION="1" SYNFUNC="subj" SYNCAT="np" SEMCAT="person" ENTITY="0"><REFEX CASE="plain" REG08-TYPE="name" ENTITY="0">Samuel Guthrie</REFEX></REF>
 (1782 - 1848) was an American physician from Hounsfield, New York. 
<REF MENTION="2" SYNFUNC="subj" SYNCAT="np" SEMCAT="person" ENTITY="0"><REFEX CASE="nominative" REG08-TYPE="pronoun" ENTITY="0">he</REFEX></REF>
 invented a form of percussion powder and also the punch lock for igniting it, which made the flintlock musket obsolete. 
<REF MENTION="3" SYNFUNC="subj" SYNCAT="np" SEMCAT="person" ENTITY="0"><REFEX CASE="nominative" REG08-TYPE="pronoun" ENTITY="0">he</REFEX></REF>
 discovered chloroform independently in 1831.
</PARAGRAPH>
